channel.title: Server up? But where are the people?
channel.description: Well here is the problem, My server is up and the ip works on it but the moparscape server status and the runelocus say that it is not on. How do I fix that :confused: My server is called spartanpkerz.no-ip.biz If you wanna check on to just make sure it's working I would be glad to let you on.

item.title: Server up? But where are the people?
item.dc:creator: @Amerks5 Amerks5
item.description:
@Amerks5 wrote:

On another topic

nah just turn your firewall off it will work trust me

No, thats a bad idea lol (no offense), your computer can get hacked (Well I got port scanned soo)

What Operating System do you have? In Vista, you need to go to Windows Firewall and open the port (Self Explanatory)

Otherwise, go to your Firewall (McAfee, Norton, etc.) and add the port there. Also, check your port forwarding, you might’ve made a mistake

Hope it helps!
